The paper focuses on text extraction, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method involves designing a neural network (cs.CL) to generate character proposals, which is a task related to object detection (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of fully convolutional networks (FCN) also suggests a focus on deep learning (cs.LG, cs.AI).
